strings: <voice_0x010018F7><se_def>Dalmatian: How do you master true magic when you're always busy with psychedelic stuff?
<voice_0x010018F9><se_def>Dalmatian: Was the mythical scepter captured at Troden Castle?
<voice_0x010018FD><se_def>Dalmatian: Chase! There's your answer! What can you make with this nutmeg?
<voice_0x010018FE><se_low>Establishing a political party: what do you do when you're not together
<voice_0x01001900><se_low>Establishing a political party: Didn't I warn you not to read books of magic without permission?
<voice_0x01001901><se_low>Establishing a political party: Not in sight! You do not understand the fundamentals of magic at all!
<voice_0x01001902><se_low>Establishing a political party: Why not follow these simple rules? I think you should train your dog. At least he'll come with me!
<voice_0x01001904><se_low>Establishing a political party: Where are you, Dalmago! come here
